rows.label: qev013804_MSG0001
rows.name: Phew! Human jobs are so so hard, aren't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0002
rows.name:
I presently work as an architect's assistant,
but I've had a lot of trouble, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_SEL0011
rows.name: Suggest that Wikae attend Alex's seminar.

rows.label: qev013804_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Wikae that you appreciate how difficult it must be.

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0003
rows.name:
Alex is holding a seminar? Wonderful!
So so wonderful...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0004
rows.name:
This will deepen my understanding of human culture
and customs, yes? Which should in turn help me
grasp your aesthetics?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0005
rows.name:
I'm eager to learn more of humans, you know?
So, yes, I think I shall attend the seminar.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0006
rows.name:
It is, but but I like humans nonetheless.
I guess the challenge...adds to my satisfaction?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0007
rows.name:
Though at times, I suppose my confidence flags,
doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0008
rows.name:
I wish there were a person or class I could consult for
help in such situations, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0009
rows.name:
Humans and Ma-non have very very different ideas of
beauty, don't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev013804_MSG0010
rows.name:
Perhaps Alex's seminar will help help me better
understand human aesthetics.[ST:wait ]
